{"id":434581,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/04/【麻辣总局】巴拿马/","date":"2016-04-08T19:05:57Z","modified":"2016-04-08T23:42:29Z","title":"【麻辣总局】《巴拿马》 (诗)","content":"<p><strong>巴拿马</strong></p>\n<p>小时候</p>\n<p>巴拿马是一条宽宽的运河</p>\n<p>太平洋在这头</p>\n<p>大西洋在那头</p>\n<p>长大后</p>\n<p>巴拿马是一个独立的国家</p>\n<p>哥伦比亚在这头</p>\n<p>哥斯达黎加在那头</p>\n<p>后来啊</p>\n<p>巴拿马是一道长长的地峡</p>\n<p>北美洲在这头</p>\n<p>南美洲在那头</p>\n<p>而现在</p>\n<p>巴拿马是一堆泄漏的文件</p>\n<p>姐夫在这头</p>\n<p>小舅子在那头</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434584\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/CffbcYeW8AATEHP.jpg-large.jpg\" alt=\"CffbcYeW8AATEHP.jpg-large\" width=\"450\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/CffbcYeW8AATEHP.jpg-large.jpg 450w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/CffbcYeW8AATEHP.jpg-large-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></p>\n<p>（参见：余光中《<a href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/subview/49129/4875629.htm\" target=\"_blank\">乡愁</a>》）</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","author":973,"categories":[18270,18269,10466,13789],"tags":[30747,30715]}